_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### What happened?\n\nWhen using `prebuilt:`, it discards the path information and only seems to preserve the `filepath.Base()` as an artifact's name.\r\n\r\nI think this is a bug, because:\r\n\r\n1. The standard Golang builder has a proper behavior: it preserves the path to a binary.\r\n2. Not preserving the path makes `strip_parent_binary_folder:` in `archive:` completely useless.\n\n### How can we reproduce this?\n\n`.goreleaser.yml` with `prebuilt:` does not preserve the path information:\r\n\r\n```yaml\r\nproject_name: tart\r\n\r\nbefore:\r\n  hooks:\r\n    - mkdir -p tart.app/Contents/MacOS\r\n    - touch tart.app/Contents/MacOS/tart\r\n\r\nbuilds:\r\n  - builder: prebuilt\r\n    goos:\r\n      - darwin\r\n    goarch:\r\n      - arm64\r\n    prebuilt:\r\n      path: tart.app/Contents/MacOS/tart\r\n\r\narchives:\r\n  - name_template: \"{{ .ProjectName }}\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n% tar tvf dist/tart.tar.gz \r\n-rwxr-xr-x  0 edi    staff       0 Jun 26 17:35 tart\r\n```\r\n\r\n`.goreleaser.yml` with standard Golang builder preserves the path information:\r\n\r\n```yaml\r\nproject_name: tart\r\n\r\nbuilds:\r\n  - goos:\r\n      - darwin\r\n    goarch:\r\n      - arm64\r\n    binary: tart.app/Contents/MacOS/tart\r\n\r\narchives:\r\n  - name_template: \"{{ .ProjectName }}\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n% tar tvf dist/tart.tar.gz                   \r\n-rwxr-xr-x  0 edi    staff 59973890 Jun 26 17:37 tart.app/Contents/MacOS/tart\r\n```\n\n### goreleaser version\n\n```bash\nRunning directly from `main` branch.\n```\n\n\n### GoReleaser Check\n\n- [X] goreleaser check shows no errors\n\n### Search\n\n- [X] I did search for other open and closed issues before opening this\n\n### Supporter\n\n- [X] I am a [sponsor](https://github.com/sponsors/caarlos0/) or a [Pro](https://goreleaser.com/pro) customer\n\n### Code of Conduct\n\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_","closed_by":{"login":"caarlos0","id":245435,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI0NTQzNQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/245435?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0","html_url":"https://github.com/caarlos0","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/4143/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/4143/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}